flowRoot.flowPara: This is your name in the conversation. Everyone else in the converstation can see your nickname.
After you have filled out the conversation name and nickname, click “connect” to start the chat.
Click on another user’s nickname to start a private chat with them. Click on the white arrow next to ther nickname to view info, send a file, or block the user.
Change status between available and away.
View the fingerprint for you and the conversation.
Turn the sound off and on.
You can put whatever you want here. Everyone you want to chat with must have the same conversation name.
